tagline: We Prove It Before You Buy

logos.name: Conservative Diagonal Blocks
logos.description: Four rectangular blocks arranged on a 45-degree diagonal axis. Two navy blocks at bottom-left, two gold blocks at upper-right. Clean geometric composition with clear progression from foundation to achievement. Has text overlay showing 'MUTED' label - may need regeneration for production use.

evaluation.colorAccuracy: Good - uses navy and gold palette
evaluation.issues: Contains text labels that shouldn't be there

logos.name: Pyramidal Stacked Blocks
logos.description: Six blocks arranged in a pyramid formation - 3 navy blocks at base, 2 muted gold blocks in middle row, 1 bright gold block at apex. Creates a strong foundational structure metaphor with clear visual hierarchy. Clean cream background.

evaluation.brandFit: Very good - conveys building, foundation, systematic growth

logos.name: Extraordinary Architectural Construction
logos.description: Sophisticated isometric architectural logo with interlocking cubic forms. Gold and navy blocks create an abstract building/tower structure with a gold pinnacle. Uses negative space and geometric interlocking to suggest construction and permanence.

evaluation.colorAccuracy: Excellent - sophisticated use of gold and navy
evaluation.brandFit: Excellent - conveys building something substantial and lasting

recommendation: blocks-2.png (Pyramidal Stacked Blocks) is recommended for its clean execution, strong foundational metaphor, and excellent brand alignment. blocks-3.png offers a more sophisticated option for premium positioning.
